        <a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/iphone/turn-on-and-practice-voiceover-iph3e2e415f/ios" target="_blank">VoiceOver</a>
        is part of iOS and
        <a href="https://support.google.com/accessibility/android/answer/6283677?hl=en" target="_blank">TalkBack</a>
